@PrivacyAnalytics.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5115

### Track endpoint — happy path (query string is stripped by middleware before the handler logs it).
POST {{PrivacyAnalytics.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/track
X-Tenant-Origin: acme.example.com
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "url": "https://shop.example.com/products/widget?email=user@example.com&ref=affiliate123",
  "referralSource": "https://google.com/search?q=widgets",
  "eventType": "pageview"
}

### Track endpoint — same tenant, expected to 429 once >100 req/sec arrive.
### Send 105 rapid requests; the last ~5 should return 429 Too Many Requests.
###
